g good governance.\n\n\u201cThe government is making efforts to bring a quality change among the lives of citizens,\u201d the head of the government said, adding that its focus was on reviving the economy affected by the pandemic, global geopolitical crisis and internal limitations for managerial skills.\n\nIn the message, he said since ancient times, Nepal has remained a symbol of religious tolerance, social harmony, and unity among various castes, languages, cultures, and civilizations, adding that such diversities were the reasons for its unique identity and self-esteem for the Nepalis.\n\nHe expressed his hope that the festival would inspire all the Nepalis to realise the needs for nation building and for promoting family happiness, social goodwill, and unity.\n\nFurthermore, he extended his wishes for joy, peace, prosperity, and sustained progress for all Nepalis within the country and abroad on the occasion of this festival.","title":"Govt effortful to bring quality change among citizens: PM Dahal","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2023/31/316588/","video":[]}
